    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028890/extras/b3564b7b55ed8b4dca8041c9019a3138.webp?t=1736815940\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028890/extras/b3564b7b55ed8b4dca8041c9019a3138.poster.avif?t=1736815940\" class=\"bb_img\" width=320 height=112 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse a land full of puzzles, people always needing your help, and dangerous foes!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Within this dynamically turn-based RPG, you'll experience riveting gameplay never before seen in the genre!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your moves push the yellow ticker to the right, and the enemies push it to the left (think of it as an epic game of tug-of-war!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every move counts! Strategize and equip the right moves to achieve victory!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make sure you don't land on any dangerous effects on the battle bar! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028890/extras/9afa48156194036dd27dc490624c8876.webp?t=1736815940\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028890/extras/9afa48156194036dd27dc490624c8876.poster.avif?t=1736815940\" class=\"bb_img\" width=320 height=96 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once upon a time... There was a mystical book powered by four crystals. This book gave anyone the will to weave the threads of reality into anything they desired. Due to a calamity of destruction it was sealed away... Until NOW!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028890/extras/072469f4cf7059b28cc25de05203f7bf.webp?t=1736815940\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028890/extras/072469f4cf7059b28cc25de05203f7bf.poster.avif?t=1736815940\" class=\"bb_img\" width=320 height=96 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mabel is a recent high school graduate with not much going on in her life—until her old friend Will called and turned everything upside down. She’s quiet, smart, and kind, always willing to help others!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028890/extras/fa698cbc01b84a507dbd8c8e6b722411.webp?t=1736815940\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028890/extras/fa698cbc01b84a507dbd8c8e6b722411.poster.avif?t=1736815940\" class=\"bb_img\" width=320 height=96 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will is a skilled mage who was born with a special bond to fire and water magic. He’s an old, close friend of Mabel and is deeply focused on finding the legendary book. He’s been obsessed with it ever since him and Mabel learned about it in a high school history class. He might not always think things through, but he never gives up!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028890/extras/15e302f2d114ed3e8655fdfb9e23312d.webp?t=1736815940\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028890/extras/15e302f2d114ed3e8655fdfb9e23312d.poster.avif?t=1736815940\" class=\"bb_img\" width=320 height=96 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nyxra is said to be a prophet destined to restore balance in the land of Cascade. Since birth, her guild has trained and prepared her to find the legendary book and its four crystals. She’s mostly distant, obsessive, and tends to overthink—but maybe her journey will help her relax a bit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
